<b>Subject:</b> I believe what he meant.....<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=710" TARGET=_self>A Correction of Geiger</A> (Platinum)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>in regards to<i> "This game doesn't inherently support senseless killing"</i> was that EQ does not support it by actually penalizing it. If you indescriminately RK (randomly kill) you will end up eventually with enough "own race" kills to cause a detrimental reaction within your home city.

<P>Keep it up and eventually you will be hated and KOS everywhere.
<P>Kill the "right" enemies, however, and a few Good Things happen...
<P>Zariin
<BR>
